#: ../../source/working_in_xsheet.rst:663
msgid ""
"Right-click in the Level Strip selection and choose **Expose in Xsheet** from "
"the menu that opens. Drawings will be exposed at the beginning of the first "
"empty column."
msgstr ""
"Hacer clic derecho en la Cinta de nivel y elegir **Exponer en planilla** en el "
